===放射性物质检测===
2009年6月{{tsl|en|Preparatory Commission for the Comprehensive Nuclear-Test-Ban Treaty Organization|全面禁止核试验条约组织(CTBTO)}}宣布，其遍布全球的40家采样站未检测出5月25日核爆炸产生的[[放射性核素|放射性核素]]。 美国宣布在日本海高空飞行的侦察机未能发现核爆炸产生的放射性物质。韩国官方也称未采集到核爆后物质。可能的原因是地下核爆炸选择了适当的围岩、足够的深度、密闭施工足够好，所以爆后产生的气体未能泄露至大气层。<ref>[[Science_(journal)|Science]], vol 324, 19 June 2009, page 1499: "[http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/summary/324/5934/1499-a Verification Experts Puzzled Over North Korea's Nuclear Test] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/summary/324/5934/1499-a |date=20090628124325 }}" by Daniel Clery</ref><ref>Jonathan Medalia, "[http://www.fas.org/sgp/crs/nuke/R41160.pdf North Korea’s 2009 Nuclear Test: Containment, Monitoring, Implications] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fas.org/sgp/crs/nuke/R41160.pdf |date=20170908040229 }}", [[Congressional_Research_Service|Congressional Research Service]] (2 April 2010).</ref>

